their accusation of lying!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2699.mp3","surahId":23,"words":[{"id":29044,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(নূহ) বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/023_026_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29045,"position":2,"arabic":"رَبِّ","translation":"\"হে আমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/023_026_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29046,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱنصُرْنِى","translation":"আমাকে সাহায্য করো","audioUrl":"wbw/023_026_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29047,"position":4,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"এ কারণে যে","audioUrl":"wbw/023_026_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29048,"position":5,"arabic":"كَذَّبُونِ","translation":"আমাকে তারা মিথ্যা সাব্যস্ত করেছে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/023_026_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29049,"position":6,"arabic":"٢٦","translation":"(২৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":27,"arabic":"فَأَوْحَيْنَآ إِلَيْهِ أَنِ ٱصْنَعِ ٱلْفُلْكَ بِأَعْيُنِنَا وَوَحْيِنَا فَإِذَا جَآءَ أَمْرُنَا وَفَارَ ٱلتَّنُّورُ ۙ فَٱسْلُكْ فِيهَا مِن كُلٍّۢ زَوْجَيْنِ ٱثْنَيْنِ وَأَهْلَكَ إِلَّا مَن سَبَقَ عَلَيْهِ ٱلْقَوْلُ مِنْهُمْ ۖ وَلَا تُخَٰطِبْنِى فِى ٱلَّذِينَ ظَلَمُوٓا۟ ۖ إِنَّهُم مُّغْرَقُونَ","translation":"Thereupon We inspired him thus: “Build, un­der Our eyes and according to Our inspiration, the ark [that shall save thee and those who follow thee]. And when Our judgment comes to pass, and waters gush forth in torrents over the face of the earth, place on board of this [ark] one pair of each [kind of animal] of either sex, as well as thy family - excepting those on whom sentence has already been passed; and do not appeal to Me [any more] in behalf of those who are bent on evildoing - for, behold, they are destined to be drowned!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2700.mp3","surahId":23,"words":[{"id":29812,"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَوْحَيْنَآ","translation":"অতঃপর আমরা ওহী করলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29813,"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِ","translation":"তার প্রতি","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29814,"position":3,"arabic":"أَنِ","translation":"\"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29815,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱصْنَعِ","translation":"নির্মাণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29816,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْفُلْكَ","translation":"নৌকা","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29817,"position":6,"arabic":"بِأَعْيُنِنَا","translation":"সামনে আমাদের চোখের","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29818,"position":7,"arabic":"وَوَحْيِنَا","translation":"ও আমাদের ওহীর ভিত্তিতে","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29819,"position":8,"arabic":"فَإِذَا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29820,"position":9,"arabic":"جَآءَ","translation":"আসবে","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29821,"position":10,"arabic":"أَمْرُنَا","translation":"আমাদের নির্দেশ","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29822,"position":11,"arabic":"وَفَارَ","translation":"ও উথলে উঠবে","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29823,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلتَّنُّورُ ۙ","translation":"চুলাটি","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29825,"position":13,"arabic":"فَٱسْلُكْ","translation":"(নৌকাতে) তখন উঠিয়ে নিবে","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29826,"position":14,"arabic":"فِيهَا","translation":"তার মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29827,"position":15,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"ধরণের","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29828,"position":16,"arabic":"كُلٍّۢ","translation":"প্রত্যেক (জীব জন্তুর)","audioUrl":"wbw/023_027_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29829,"position":17,"arabic":"زَوْجَيْنِ","tra